Title : Template:Footin-f2/doc
Text : {{documentation subpage}}
{{subst only}}
==Usage==
Use this template combined with [[Wikipedia:Template substitution|subst]] to give a "Football in" link of the given country and its flagicon. It is not designed to be used as a pure template call and should never be used without substitution.

<code><nowiki>{{subst:footin-f2|</nowiki>''country name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>

===Example===
The input <code><nowiki>{{subst:footin-f2|England}}</nowiki></code> gives {{flagicon|England}} [[Football in England|England]].

